title: **__Security Verification & Rules__**
description:
**Rules**
**1. Respect fellow members**
No verbal or any other form of abuse is tolerate at all.

**2. No drama**
Starting arguments or any other toxic behaviour in or out of game

**3. No discussion of politics or religion**
Try to keep your opinions to yourself

**4. No racism or discrimination of any kind**
We are all for inclusivity here, any kind of racism/discrimination will result in an instant ban

**5. No NSFW content**
We want a clean discord and many users use this server while at work

**6. Use the appropiate channels**
Such as advertising in <#673436198751961088>

**7. No mic spamming**
Includes the use of soundboards when used too frequently

**8. No Multi-Claning**
Unless it's in games that we are not officially in

----------------------------------------
Please **__react__** to the :ballot_box_with_check:  below to **gain access** to this server.

This is used for security purposes

By reacting, you **accept our rules** and ensure that you follow them
failure to do could result in disciplinary action
----------------------------------------
If you don't know how to react, please follow this clip.
